text:
Non-HubSpot forms doesn’t have an API, so any attempt would be hacking it together. 

You’re probably better off submitting to the Forms API. 
• docs -<https://legacydocs.HubSpot.com/docs/methods/forms/submit_form|https://legacydocs.HubSpot.com/docs/methods/forms/submit_form>
• A tutorial I wrote that’s geared towards a custom form, but could be helpful <https://gist.github.com/robertainslie/b110b8275beee1b27255c4d6e2ba2e8c|https://gist.github.com/robertainslie/b110b8275beee1b27255c4d6e2ba2e8c>
